          <div><span class="text-terminal-dim">Profesión:</span> Desarrollador Full Stack</div>
          <div><span class="text-terminal-dim">Email:</span> webmaster@gusi.dev</div>
          <div>
            <span class="text-terminal-dim">GitHub:</span>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/Gusi-ui"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-terminal-text hover:text-terminal-bright underline">github.com/Gusi-ui</a
